storeItems.name: Quinn's
storeItems.description: You visited Quinn's Music last time in July '20. The store manager's name is Joseph and the sales rep for the guitar department is Annette. Quinn's Music ordered 11 guitars and 2 drum sets last month and has paid all invoices on time. Their clientele consists mostly of heavy metal bands but also some jazz musicians frequent the place. The new EG-18275 Metal guitar line will likely resonate with the sales associates in this store. Make sure to pitch those.
